{"hablante":"A","texto":"Do you have brothers or sisters?"},
{"hablante":"B","texto":"I have one sister. Her name is Sofia."},
{"hablante":"A","texto":"Is she married?"},
{"hablante":"B","texto":"No, she's single."},
{"hablante":"A","texto":"And this? Is it your dog?"},
{"hablante":"B","texto":"Yes, that's my dog. His name is Max."}
